casebody.data:
No. 09-490. Mayo Collaborative Services, dba Mayo Medical Laboratories, et al., Petitioners v. Prometheus Laboratories, Inc. 561 U.S. 1040, 130 S. Ct. 3543,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1120,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5537. June 29, 2010.

Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Federal Circuit for further consideration in light of Bilski v. Kappos, 561 U.S. 593, 130 S. Ct. 3218, 177 L. Ed. 2d 792 (2010).

Same case below, 581 F.3d 1336.
